## Additional Notice

The workflows, reference files, and domain knowledge contained in this
repository are provided for operational assistance only. They do not
constitute licensed engineering advice, legal advice, or a substitute for
review by a licensed professional.

Structural calculations require sign-off by a licensed structural or
civil engineer. Electrical designs require sign-off by a licensed electrical
engineer or contractor in the applicable jurisdiction. Permit submissions
are the responsibility of the licensed contractor of record.

AHJ requirements, fire codes, and electrical codes change. The reference
files in this repository reflect conditions as of the dates noted within
each file. Users are responsible for verifying current requirements with
the applicable Authority Having Jurisdiction before submitting any permit
application.

Tariff rates, trade policies, and procurement conditions change. The
tariff reference file reflects conditions as of early 2026. Users are
responsible for confirming current tariff exposure with a licensed customs
broker or trade compliance advisor before executing procurement decisions.

Fractional Build accepts no liability for permit rejections, procurement
errors, construction defects, or any other outcome arising from the use
of the workflows and reference materials in this repository.
